Raspi-Edge
==========

Welcome to Raspy-Edge, the Raspberry Pi Edge-Router distribution.

The official installer supports Linux on Raspberry Pi and Banana Pi, arm-hf architectures.

Features
--------

  * IPv6 support with 6lowpan and rpl routing

What Raspi-Edge contains
------------------------
Raspi-Edge currently comes with the following software:

  * tunslip6
  * radvd
  


Quick introduction
------------------

The following example illustrates how simple Raspi-Edge is to use. First install the package matching your operating system:

# sudo sh edge_install_script.sh

have fun :-)

